'''Psionics''' (from ''[[Psychic]]'' + ''[[Electronics]]'') is the science and technology of [[Psi_Energy|psi phenomena]] — the intersection of consciousness, electromagnetic biology, scalar field theory, and higher-dimensional physics. In the [[Natra|Natura]] universe, psionics is both a natural phenomenon governed by a rigorous equation set and a technology domain explored through [[Psi_Tech]].

This page is the canonical 4D equation reference. For the deeper 5D origin see [[5D_Action_Principle]]; for plain-language entry see [[Psionics_Primer]]; for the symbol-only reference see [[Symbol_Glossary]].

