* '''Anomalous cognition:''' [[Ganzfeld_Procedure|Ganzfeld]] meta-analyses (Bem & Honorton 1994; Storm 2010), [[PEAR_Program|PEAR]] 2.5-million-trial REG dataset, [[Presentiment]] (Mossbridge et al. 2012 meta-analysis).

